            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the yeast has developed, add your <strong>pizza base mix</strong>, <strong>nigella seeds </strong>and<strong> half </strong>your<strong> natural yoghurt </strong>(save the rest for later!) to the bowl with the yeast</p><p>Gradually add up to 60ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[80ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]</span> <strong>warm water </strong>(you may not need all of it), a little at a time, and gently mix with a plastic spatula until a sticky dough ball has formed</p><p>Tip the <strong>dough</strong> out onto a<strong> lightly floured </strong>work surface and knead it for 20 secs, then set aside – this is your <strong>naan dough</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1695994847918-x200.jpg",
