            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>naan</strong> <strong>dough</strong> into 1 ball per person, then roll each <strong>dough ball</strong> out with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> into a circular disc – this is your<strong> naan</strong></p><p>Transfer the <strong>chicken bhuna curry </strong>to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> (use individual ones for fancy presentation!) and top with the <strong>naan</strong></p><p>Tip: Only have one oven-proof dish? Leave the naan dough whole and roll out to the size of your dish!</p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 15-18 min or until the naan is cooked through</p>",
      "order": 6,
