    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>garlic naan topped chicken bhuna pie</strong> with the <strong>green</strong> <strong>beans</strong> to the side</p><p>Serve the<strong> remaining natural yoghurt </strong>in a pot to the side to drizzle all over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
